PhysicalTable.name: SAMP_EMPL_D_VH
PhysicalTable.Description: Employee Dimension table: Stores employee dimension attribute information

PhysicalColumn.name: Mgr_Id
PhysicalColumn.Description: Manager Id: Stores manager id as an integer

PhysicalColumn.name: Empl_Name
PhysicalColumn.Description: Employee Name: Stores employee name as a text

PhysicalColumn.name: Employee_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Employee Key: Surrogate key of the employee dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Postn_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Position Key: Joins to Postn_key in employee position dimension table

PhysicalColumn.name: Hire_Dt
PhysicalColumn.Description: Hire Date: Stores employee hire date information in date format

PhysicalColumn.name: Type
PhysicalColumn.Description: Type: Stores employee type information as text
